\subtree{\title{JLCPCB Order Audit (2026-04-13 to 2026-04-15)}
\taxon{remark}
\import{macros}

\p{Two PCBA orders (12291944A-Y4 for Uncut Gem, 12291944A-Y2 for fNIRS ECU) were cancelled by JLCPCB QA (Sunny) due to missing solder mask layers in the initial gerber export. Root cause: Altium-to-KiCad conversion dropped F_Mask and B_Mask layers. Fixed gerbers re-exported 2026-04-13, archived at assets/gerbers/opennirscap-v2/.}

